com.transifex.common

Class LocaleData.LocaleStrings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.transifex.common.LocaleData.LocaleStrings
  • Enclosing class:
    LocaleData

    public static class LocaleData.LocaleStrings
extends Object
    A class holding some locale's strings. It maps String keys to LocaleData.StringInfo objects.

    • Constructor Detail

      • LocaleStrings

        public LocaleStrings(@NonNull
                     HashMap<String,LocaleData.StringInfo> map)
        Creates a LocaleStrings object which uses the provided HashMap.

        The HashMap should map Android resource entry names to LocaleData.StringInfo objects like this: 

            {
        'key1' : LocaleString,
        'key2' : LocaleString,
    }
